@CsvIngestionApi_HostAddress = https://localhost:7211

### Health check (anonymous - no token needed)
GET {{CsvIngestionApi_HostAddress}}/api/ping
Accept: application/json

### Upload a CSV file to blob storage (multipart/form-data)
POST {{CsvIngestionApi_HostAddress}}/api/csv/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----CsvBoundary

------CsvBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

id,name,value
1,alpha,100
2,beta,200
3,gamma,300
------CsvBoundary--

###
